I need to identify and extract the expense item from the statement of profit or loss and other comprehensive income.

Looking at the balance sheet provided, I need to find expense-related line items. In accounting, accumulated depreciation represents the total depreciation expense that has been recorded over time.

In the balance sheet, I can see:
- Accumulated Depreciation with an initial amount of 0.00 on 2023-12-31
- Accumulated Depreciation with an end amount of 96479.34 on 2024-02-04

This accumulated depreciation represents an expense that has been incurred over the period.

Therefore:

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '96479.34'}}
```
